&lt;li&gt;Providing regular market, economic, and portfolio updates to clients, prospects, and centers of influence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee, mentor, and develop Analysts and other team members&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Chief Investment Officer to participate in strategic research and portfolio evaluation initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
